Text: Who Has Room for Cash Palm Solutions brought to you by InSync Online Who Has Room For Cash Dear Jess Shopping lists checks credit cards PINs user names passwords photos of your little ones With all the stuff you carry in your wallet whos got room for cash For a solution to the overstuffed wallet syndrome we happily point you to SplashWallet Suite This virtual wallet for your Palmtm handheld is actually four applications in one SplashShopper keeps lists of groceries to buy movies to rent CDs to buy books to read and more SplashID keeps all your user names passwords and other ID info in one secure place SplashMoney records your checking and credit card transactions and tracks your account balances And SplashPhoto makes an excellent digital brag book for your walletsize photos Purchase the entire SplashWallet Suite versus one app at a time and youll save a bundle For pricing and other details visit Splashdatacom udkfNmPOZecKrw The InSync Online Team The content of this message is based on your personal InSync Online profile To modify your profile or unsubscribe from InSync Online return to your InSync Online profile by clicking on the link below Or unsubscribe by replying to this message with unsubscribe as the subject line of the message Palm makes no warranty as to the claims made by the thirdparty about this product C Palm Inc All rights reserved udrEfNmPOZecKrxQ Palmcom udzkfNmPOZecKrxV Palm Store udzEfNmPOZecKrxK InSync Online insyncdynisZVae MyPalm udukfNmPOZecKrxE
